{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC01_WIL_060.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1a,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x199,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hellooo? Ayesha, are you here?<CR>I came to play."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Bell, welcome. What are you doing here today?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I came to watch you synthesize.<CR>Has the book I gave you helped any?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yup. I learned a lot of useful information."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Well, that's good. That book was too difficult... I mean, it was about an irrelevant field for me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "If it's helping you, I'm glad I passed it on to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "But I still have some doubts.<CR>I don't think I'm an alchemist..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Are you still saying that? You're really particular about the small stuff."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Well, it's because that book described alchemists as great people."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I'm not that great of a person by any stretch of the imagination."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x168,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, now that you mention it...<CR>Amazingly...you have no gravitas."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha... So even when I'm told that I'm an alchemist, it still doesn't feel right."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x16b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Well, I don't think you need to get stuck on the small details."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Why don't we just say you're an<CR>apothecary who can also do alchemy,<CR>and leave it at that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I-I see...! That does feel more comfortable!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I guess I shouldn't have been too worried about something as small as my job title..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "In reality, you should worry about it. It's important to know who you are."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I always try to keep in mind that I'm a witch."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "So that someday, I can be a great witch, just like my great-great-grandmother!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "You're thinking that far ahead?<CR>Bell, you're amazing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, it's not that amazing. Feel free to consult with me anytime!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Training a junior is the job of a senior!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Huuuh? I'm your junior?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "That's right. I told you that witches and alchemists are like relatives, didn't I?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "So, you're my junior!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I see. Then I'll be counting on you."
        }
    ]
}